      <title>莫迪对印度国有企业的改革正在吸引充满希望的投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/india-state-firms-stock-rally-extends-in-part-due-to-modi-s-governance-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度的国营企业长期以来因长期效率低下和官僚机构僵化而臭名昭著，这使得它们成为许多投资者的禁忌，尽管它们在亚洲第三大经济体的几个主要行业中占据主导地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/india-state-firms-stock-rally-extends-in-part-due-to-modi-s-governance-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
